{"tid":2510403,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"衞蘭算唔算係香港開埠以嚟最令人失望嘅歌手？","createTime":"2021-04-30T06:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T06:53:28.000Z","uid":20032,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b547c0e62784cfc5e51882b362f43759680c83","tid":2510403,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:45:01.000Z","msg":"佢咁嘅實力紅唔起真係好令人失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道講到依到一定有人話好紅喎，個個識<br />\n<br />\n又開紅館又Full之類<br />\n<br />\n但你比起楊千嬅開左十鳩幾次紅館<br />\n<br />\n衞蘭好明顯有料好多，但都未做到過其他天后級有嘅待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知紅依個字好難定義，但我知道佢肯定唔夠Joey千嬅紅<br />\n<br />\n佢歌又紅，<br />\n大哥，殘酷遊戲，街燈晚餐，就算世界無童話，首首都XX人口，有乜可能咁嘅成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前嘅新生代，依家嘅中生代肯定係Gem1Jan2<br />\n<br />\n反觀人地Gem就紅到上NASA<br />\n衞蘭都只係仲得到人實力上嘅認可<br />\n<br />\n公平咩"},{"pid":"ceab958ceea274b08bf2969d8ed29e42e9cd77b2","tid":2510403,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:45:39.000Z","msg":"嬲得滯無講埋佢唱live嘅實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b99fa0a1d4c190a0445bccb8df6e334963ebd8","tid":2510403,"uid":33222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:49:11.000Z","msg":"我頭先心入面唱住大哥打開連登，一打開就見到呢個post"},{"pid":"df2dd4a75b8a31bcea26d557f14e67751f050da4","tid":2510403,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89b99fa0a1d4c190a0445bccb8df6e334963ebd8","tid":2510403,"uid":33222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:49:11.000Z","msg":"我頭先心入面唱住大哥打開連登，一打開就見到呢個post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:49:49.000Z","msg":"Big Brother is watching you<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930b4cdef5fc95da0c7ed7ae89cfce852763dfc3","tid":2510403,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:50:18.000Z","msg":"跟錯老闆"},{